<br>
It's a minimal difference on a skill that only has a minor effect in combat anyway.<br>
<br>
VI is upping our dodge skill, albeit the hybrids are getting a boost that is larger than ours by a patheticly small margin.  VI is changing our mitigation in some (currently unknown) circumstances (yes, the other plate classes get it too).  VI is improving Taunt.  VI changed Warcry so maybe it isn't completely useless now, although, maybe it still is.<br>
<br>
If you want to bitch, there are plenty of other things to bitch about than one damn percentage point.  At least give VI some credit for listening and making some POSITIVE changes!<br>
<br>
/rant on<br>
<br>
It's one @$&amp;#ing percentage point!  I truly doubt that this is suddenly going to change the balance between warriors and hybrids, making warriors an unplayable class!<br>
<br>
/rant off<br>
